    <item>
      <title>美国将在特朗普之前敲定 Rivian 和 Plug 的数十亿美元融资计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/us-to-finalize-billions-in-funding-for-rivian-plug-before-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，拜登政府准备在下周特朗普政府上台之前，为电动汽车制造商 Rivian Automotive Inc. 和氢能制造商 Plug Power Inc. 完成数十亿美元的融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/us-to-finalize-billions-in-funding-for-rivian-plug-before-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 02:17:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>报告称财政部黑客专注于制裁和情报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/treasury-hackers-focused-on-sanctions-intelligence-report-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博新闻社看到的一份机构报告显示，受中国政府支持的黑客入侵了美国财政部，入侵了 400 多台笔记本电脑和台式电脑，尤其对负责制裁、国际事务和情报工作的工作人员和高级领导人的机器感兴趣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/treasury-hackers-focused-on-sanctions-intelligence-report-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 01:57:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登在告别演讲中提到“极端财富”带来的威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/biden-warns-of-threat-from-extreme-wealth-in-farewell-address</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登周三在椭圆形办公室发表告别演讲时警告美国人，“权力危险地集中在”极少数超级富豪手中，他担心此举会对国家的民主产生影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/biden-warns-of-threat-from-extreme-wealth-in-farewell-address</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 01:36:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港考虑第二年提高高收入者税负</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/hong-kong-weighs-raising-taxes-on-top-earners-for-second-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，香港政府正在研究连续第二年对香港高收入者提高税收，以弥补预算赤字。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/hong-kong-weighs-raising-taxes-on-top-earners-for-second-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 01:15:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝塞特表示美元的全球地位对美国经济至关重要</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/bessent-will-say-dollar-s-status-is-critical-to-us-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据准备好的讲稿，唐纳德·特朗普提名的财政部长候选人斯科特·贝森特将向参议院委员会表示，维持美元作为世界储备资产的地位对美国经济健康和国家未来至关重要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/bessent-will-say-dollar-s-status-is-critical-to-us-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 00:47:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的环保选择为马斯克支持的倡导组织带来了好处</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/trump-s-environmental-pick-worked-for-musk-backed-advocacy-group</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据新的道德披露文件显示，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普选择的环境保护署署长李·泽尔丁曾担任多家保守派组织的顾问，其中包括伊隆·马斯克青睐的黑钱倡导组织之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/trump-s-environmental-pick-worked-for-musk-backed-advocacy-group</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 00:36:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>约翰逊解除特纳众议院情报委员会主席职务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/speaker-johnson-removes-turner-as-head-of-house-intelligence-committee</link>
      <description><![CDATA[众议院议长迈克·约翰逊表示，长期担任国防鹰派的众议员迈克·特纳已被免去众议院情报委员会主席的职务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/speaker-johnson-removes-turner-as-head-of-house-intelligence-committee</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 23:53:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大被竞争对手指控倾销乳制品</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/canada-accused-by-rival-dairy-exporters-of-dumping-milk-products</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰、澳大利亚和美国乳制品公司指责加拿大向国际市场倾销低价乳制品，并要求其政府进行干预。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/canada-accused-by-rival-dairy-exporters-of-dumping-milk-products</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 21:26:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢比奥称美国应重新考虑雪佛龙在委内瑞拉的交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/rubio-says-us-should-reconsider-chevron-s-oil-deal-in-venezuela</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普的国务卿提名人马可·卢比奥表示，美国应该重新考虑允许雪佛龙公司在委内瑞拉运营的制裁豁免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/rubio-says-us-should-reconsider-chevron-s-oil-deal-in-venezuela</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 20:40:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台积电在中美脱钩进程中对美、日投资创纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/taiwan-investments-in-us-japan-surge-as-china-figure-stagnates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年，台湾企业对美国和日本的投资创下了历史新高，而对中国大陆的投资则停滞不前——凸显了技术竞争和两岸关系恶化导致的供应链转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/taiwan-investments-in-us-japan-surge-as-china-figure-stagnates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 09:40:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
